<db:para>Although this little application does not look much like a fully-fledged modern GUI application, it uses many of the basic elements that are used in more complex applications. After you have worked through this tutorial, we recommend reading the <db:link xlink:href="qtwidgets-mainwindows-application-example.xml">Application</db:link> example, which presents a small GUI application, with menus, toolbars, a status bar, and so on.</db:para>
